    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/d15ef0ba13dc639f63c4944f2e236f83.poster.avif?t=1573135497\" width=624 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/d15ef0ba13dc639f63c4944f2e236f83.webm?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/d15ef0ba13dc639f63c4944f2e236f83.mp4?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打造HYPERGUN！</strong></h2><br>在HYPERGUN中，扮演科技开发实验室里的无畏实习生“杜威·欧文斯”来拯救世界！这是一款以一个效能差强人意的程序性武器为中心，并且节奏明快的roguelite射击游戏，就看杜威是否能掌握终极战斗模拟器。 玩家们可在为打造终极武器而设计的模拟中，勇闯一波又一波的外星入侵者，并在打造HYPERGUN的旅程中解锁激动人心的新职业和习得强大技能！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/e031f52ba316c0abcab8219953790f38.poster.avif?t=1573135497\" width=624 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/e031f52ba316c0abcab8219953790f38.webm?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/e031f52ba316c0abcab8219953790f38.mp4?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>节奏明快，FPS Roguelite游戏玩法<br></li><li>打造HYPERGUN - 超过150种武器模块可供收集，让您在模拟中每一次的体验都独一无二。您获得的每个模块将会以激动人心，或有时却令人质疑的方式改变您的武器，这全是为了找出击败外星压迫者的终极武器。<br></li><li>程序关卡 - 勇闯每一次都会随机生成、难度逐渐提升的模拟竞技场。<br></li><li>外星族群 - 对抗一群以完美无瑕的细节再造的凶残外星入侵者（模拟）。<br></li><li>凶狠强大的Boss - 挑战每一关卡结束前会出现的超级强大boss，借此考验您的技巧与测试您的武器。<br></li><li>可解锁的职业与技能 - 解锁同事的模拟人物，以获得40多种独特技能供您选择，让您在模拟中稳占上风。<br></li><li>办公室政治 - 扮演实习生杜威·欧文斯，在周末设法潜入并探索科技开发办公室。即便是世界末日，也依然有时间追查同事们那些贬低人的便利贴。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/586d7fbc46e8a2d7d6a5868ecd0968a6.poster.avif?t=1573135497\" width=624 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/586d7fbc46e8a2d7d6a5868ecd0968a6.webm?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/586d7fbc46e8a2d7d6a5868ecd0968a6.mp4?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>您的任务</strong></h2><br>这是2038年，地球已被一个非常先进的外星种族占领。 人类正处于崩溃的边缘，他们的命运如今取决于绝密的HYPERGUN计划：一种极其先进的模拟，旨在通过无数次模拟中的武器组件拼合，来打造对抗外星压迫者的终极武器。<br><br>科技开发实验室的实习生“杜威·欧文斯”成功在周末潜入设施中（即便是世界末日，我们也依然需要享受一下周末！）。 他是想向顽固不化的首席执行官“罗杰”证明自己，还是他在酝酿着什么阴谋呢？我们或许永远不会知道，但他也可能就这样拯救了全世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/0596507637e42088333844a35a242458.poster.avif?t=1573135497\" width=624 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/0596507637e42088333844a35a242458.webm?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/783450/extras/0596507637e42088333844a35a242458.mp4?t=1573135497\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
